Detailed Description

cvmx_l2c_ver_msc

L2C_VER_MSC = L2C Virtualization Miscellaneous Error Register (not in 63xx pass 1.x)

Description: records type of command associated with HOLEWR/BIGWR/VRTWR/VRTIDRNG/VRTADRNG interrupts
